data.description: GORGEOUS and completely UPDATED 2,040 sq foot townhome with 3 bedrooms and 3 full baths. You will LOVE the NEW HVAC, copper wiring, breaker box, pex piping, water softener, appliances, water heater, flooring, paint, cabinets, showers, tub, sinks, toilets, light fixtures, custom draperies, gate, countertops, backsplash & more!! This unique property has 2 living areas, designer open kitchen, fireplace and a full bath downstairs. This home boasts lots of storage. The closets have built-ins.  A new garage with new garage door, opener, lighting and vent fan was added. This quiet unit overlooks a lovely courtyard and has a patio. The HOA dues cover water, sewer, trash, tennis courts and grounds.  Great location in upfront Kingwood. This home is zoned to outstanding Kingwood schools and is close to shopping, restaurants, parks and trails. NO FLOODING!! You need to see to appreciate this beautiful home!! A MUST SEE!!
